                    <p>2.  Use the tabs to navigate through different ranking categories.</p>
                    <p>3.  Click on a country name in the ranking list to access the country profile.</p>
                    <p>[INSERT SCREESHOT 12]</p>
                    <p>4.  Select the Settings button to adjust the minimum tree cover canopy density.</p>
                    <p>5.  Learn more about or share each graph by selecting the information or share icons.</p>
                    <p>[INSERT SCREESHOT 13]</p>
